  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to check if Naloxone induce an inhibiting effect on the analgesic
      effect of paracetamol in healthy volunteer, using evoked potentials.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Double Blind, cross-over study in healthy volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
